desc=Elves are a slender race, with both males and females standing around five feet tall and weighing around 130 pounds. Most have dark hair, with little or no body or facial hair. Their skin is pale, and they have pointed ears and delicate features. Elves are lithe and graceful, with keen eyesight and hearing. Elves are typically inquisitive, passionate, self-assured, and sometimes haughty. Their typical lifespan is a dozen centuries or more.//Elves may become most classes excluding Barbarian and Assassin, and they are also able to take the combination classes of Fightermage (Fighter plus Magic-User) and Magethief (Thief plus Illusionist). Elves never roll larger than d6 for hit points, regardless of their class.//All Elves have Darkvision with a 60' range. They are so observant that they can find secret doors with even a cursory glance. Elves are immune to the paralyzing attack of ghouls, and are less likely to be surprised in combat.


