desc=Hobgoblins are the larger cousins of goblins, being about the same size as humans. Their hair colors range from dark reddish-brown to dark gray, and their skin tones are usually red or orange. A hobgoblin's eyes are yellowish or dark brown. Hobgoblins keep their weapons keenly polished and in good repair.//Hobgoblins are cruel and calculating warriors, always looking to exploit those weaker than themselves. They have a strong grasp of strategy and tactics and are capable of carrying out sophisticated battle plans. Under the leadership of a skilled strategist or tactician, their discipline can prove a deciding factor. Hobgoblins hate Elves and attack them first in preference over other opponents. Hobgoblin deities reinforce this militaristic outlook, and their Clerics are able to favor additional weapons as a result, such as the Spear, BattleAxe and Longsword.//While not as mechanically-minded as normal goblins, a hobgoblin is still very alert, noticing secret doors as well as an Elf. Like most dark-dwelling races, a hobgoblin has Darkvision out to 60'.

